==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: affirmative action
<hw>affirmative action</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a policy of
making active efforts to improve the employment or educational
opportunities available to members of minority groups or women; --
achieved by employers or schools by using various techniques, but
excluding the use of simple quotas or outright discrimination against
white males.</def> <note>affirmative action is required by law for
certain employers in the United States.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Affirmatively</ent>⟦br⟧
